    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super reliable, and it still drives beautifully! It\u2019s been well-maintained and is ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that still feels fresh and fun, this is the one for you. Send me a message, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut and communicative, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M-Variable differential lock for optimized lateral dynamics. This example has been fastidiously maintained with recent preventative service on the throttle actuators and a comprehensive fluid flush using 10W-60 synthetic. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, and the subframe bushings and mounting points have been inspected to ensure structural integrity. A mechanically robust specimen ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
