    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in great shape and runs like a dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so you\u2019re getting a solid vehicle without the 'new car' price tag. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
