    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis remains sharp with recent bushing refreshes and Bilstein dampers, while the critical rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced. Though the exterior shows light patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronicity and compression across all cylinders remain excellent. A true enthusiast\u2019s specimen maintained for peak lateral and longitudinal performance.",
